    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This ornate doorknob can open doors both material and metaphysical, revealing dreams and nightmares. The spell DC of any spell cast by activating this item is 20. \n* **Armor** You gain a +1 item bonus to Thievery checks to Pick a Lock.\n* **Weapon** If you critically succeed at a Strike with the weapon, the target is dazzled until the end of its next turn.",
